article.title: Tech billionaires cashed out $16 billion in 2025 as stocks soared
article.summary: Jeff Bezos led the way. The Amazon founder sold 25 million shares for $5.7 billion in June and July, right around the time he was getting hitched to Lauren Sanchez in Venice.
